{"tid":4411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[網絡小說15年年資]起點小說推介","createTime":"2016-11-26T13:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T04:08:33.000Z","uid":18676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5eea9ee2c226e2e1c7290e03031c58f1461c886b","tid":4411,"uid":18676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0D35k0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0D35k0.jpg&h=3b0ee21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家追緊呢幾套小說<br />\n<br />\n同各位巴絲分享下依家有咩小說值得我追，<br />\n睇左咁耐小說，普通yy 小說已經吸引唔再我去睇，<br />\n仲有廣電局既限制，好多野都唔俾寫，e.g. 婚外情，性愛場面，種馬，政治，粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到好多故事都失色不少，題材亦大受限制。。。<br />\n大家都可以講下有咩小說好睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/163781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F163781.jpg&h=ad6989e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我真是大明星<br />\n<br />\n排行榜第一名，講男主角轉左去另一個冇現今娛樂文化既世界，跟手將世界各樣名著搬出黎，<br />\n屌打其他人，學到唔同詩詞歌賦，知更多大陸興既事物，爽文👍🏻"},{"pid":"a147103535722b3f5522ba5b5468582b278b2393","tid":4411,"uid":441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:25:25.000Z","msg":"咩app? 以前真係咩題材都有"},{"pid":"b5c1004fde51707c0930f86d4f5a4f43ae3269fb","tid":4411,"uid":18676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩app? 以前真係咩題材都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起點 app<br />\n<br />\n大陸最大既小說網（好似係）<br />\n<br />\n開頭唔知幾多萬字既小說係免費既，之後就每1000字3分（好似係） 咁收錢，<br />\n睇完一部超長篇小說都係幾十蚊"},{"pid":"8dee1c42b184acf71eb5253330b35d0bd80c7ba1","tid":4411,"uid":18676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/213104_7b6e052a1b79952edccbfeff96b480f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F213104_7b6e052a1b79952edccbfeff96b480f5.jpg&h=8d09ebb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元氣少年<br />\n<br />\n大神張君仔既作品，<br />\n超級教師個作者，<br />\n同廖學兵差唔多，都係屈其他人機，<br />\n但今次有多重人格呢個gimmick<br />\n同埋佢有教人提升自己，<br />\n唔好淨係打機做宅男，<br />\n我都係因為佢開始練靚手字，<br />\n唔想浪費時間淨係睇小說，漫畫，電影<br />\n<br />\n其實我依家睇既小說大多係大神出品，<br />\n所以我先會去睇，<br />\n因為佢地既作品陪住我成長，由中學，讀u <br />\n再到出黎做野"},{"pid":"2d8058e61335a356021765f1573d189d70e74a71","tid":4411,"uid":18676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/213851_1642640f8cd598f60d59b7edc2e6010d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F213851_1642640f8cd598f60d59b7edc2e6010d.jpg&h=3c279ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紫川作者寫既<br />\n今次佢較多墨跡係官場生活，<br />\n打鬥比較少<br />\n雖然佢更新比較慢同唔定時，但佢可以寫到好吸引我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54S61k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54S61k.jpg&h=56b8d9bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢本係末世小說，但有別於其他末世小說，<br />\n開創自己既末世格局，<br />\n描寫末世開始既畫面同升上天一刻俾我一種驚豔既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wr912R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwr912R.jpg&h=a79f4e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跳舞作品，<br />\n不多講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/214412_45918b75ef016b64701cc9502a41fa08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F214412_45918b75ef016b64701cc9502a41fa08.jpg&h=e449eec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡徒作者<br />\n極品小說，每次講到松間城，都令我熱血沸騰，<br />\n佢亦開創元力世界觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb9909f043a162a0fbda2276419a3cd07241d0a","tid":4411,"uid":18313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"好耐無睇大陸小說了"},{"pid":"430adbb0b471bda1546c53edee5e783ea0c661bc","tid":4411,"uid":18676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好耐無睇大陸小說了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜台灣市場收左皮，冇一個好既小說網<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩好推介？"},{"pid":"26475d6c4d87a33031cd23db71067715a6f31046","tid":4411,"uid":31700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好耐無睇大陸小說了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜台灣市場收左皮，冇一個好既小說網<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩好推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n修真聊天群（好好笑超好笑一定要睇<br />\n傭兵的戰爭（現代戰爭寫得好好<br />\n異常生物見聞錄（有睇希靈帝國就要睇埋<br />\n奧術神座（經典<br />\n<br />\n台灣有一本好記得，叫網遊夢境生活（主角毒拎玩ai"},{"pid":"fef6c0ab311ad5abdc92e050a25be27284996242","tid":4411,"uid":77046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"竟然一套我睇緊既都冇 五行天都會睇既遲d<br />\n<br />\n依家我追緊幾本都ok<br />\n驚悚樂園<br />\n武煉巔峰<br />\n擇天記<br />\n雪鷹領主"},{"pid":"f0e84ba4dba3d6ce48a93881959ca0ed09950399","tid":4411,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"唔想睇殘體字"},{"pid":"c0e180f57916dc5664ff98f218324a7adc74bc4e","tid":4411,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"唔怪得宜家啲書咁悶，原來咁多限制<br />\n推舊書la，宜家啲新書咁垃圾"},{"pid":"fbcf8918289edc132bbf568a625fe95b18fe6699","tid":4411,"uid":5148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"追過好多套<br />\n而家追緊<br />\n武煉巔峰<br />\n大主宰<br />\n最強反派系統<br />\n<br />\n不過個人認為龍戰士正傳冇人超越到"},{"pid":"2582fc8321d19184395da2125c5d1a5423cf69d4","tid":4411,"uid":76449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/020813_dace7548429f42912c8f3b03d3644b47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F020813_dace7548429f42912c8f3b03d3644b47.jpg&h=07a61888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇緊呢度"},{"pid":"7d64b28e6d80f0e093c176583803d5638adde330","tid":4411,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/020813_dace7548429f42912c8f3b03d3644b47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F020813_dace7548429f42912c8f3b03d3644b47.jpg&h=07a61888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇緊呢度</blockquote><br />\n岩岩用左1星期多少少時間睇哂全職法師,有無其他類似既推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c3b4cdbfdf26a13ab51b1d18ac4e6f5bc20607","tid":4411,"uid":56225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"有無小說係講主角由頭廢到尾+無奇遇幸運屬性負數"},{"pid":"98686e6678a575c0f5cca2fdacbac1f5feaa02d6","tid":4411,"uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無小說係講主角由頭廢到尾+無奇遇幸運屬性負數</blockquote><br />\n我的女兒我的天使<br />\n由頭到尾虐主，突出單親養女兒既辛苦，主角能力唔算強，但係品格完美"},{"pid":"bf8c1d9ef727a294503baafc91fc0b1fcf451603","tid":4411,"uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"垃圾起點，睇緊本書 (算卦我靠玩微信) 好好地，比佢河蟹到廢左"}]}